Message.SourceString: I see you've started to get a little green around the thumbs! Farming will make survival on Ashenfall a little less horrible.
Message.LocalizedString: I see you've started to get a little green around the thumbs! Farming will make survival on Ashenfall a little less horrible.

Message.SourceString: You'll be able to grow fruits, vegetables, and all manner of plants. Food, potion ingredients and perhaps some crafting resources too!
Message.LocalizedString: You'll be able to grow fruits, vegetables, and all manner of plants. Food, potion ingredients and perhaps some crafting resources too!

Message.SourceString: Oh? You've overburdened yourself with all the random things you can cram in your pockets. Come back and see me when you've made a bit of room.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh? You've overburdened yourself with all the random things you can cram in your pockets. Come back and see me when you've made a bit of room.

Message.SourceString: Look at you, practically master farmer already. Farming is a wonderful way to keep yourself well fed, and with access to useful materials.
Message.LocalizedString: Look at you, practically master farmer already. Farming is a wonderful way to keep yourself well fed, and with access to useful materials.

Message.SourceString: Speaking of useful, here, take this. My little gift to you. Just don't tell the others, they'll get all jealous again.
Message.LocalizedString: Speaking of useful, here, take this. My little gift to you. Just don't tell the others, they'll get all jealous again.

Message.SourceString: Anything else I can help you with?
Message.LocalizedString: Anything else I can help you with?

Message.SourceString: Oh? You've overburdened yourself with all the random things you can cram in your pockets. Come back and see me when you've made a bit of room.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh? You've overburdened yourself with all the random things you can cram in your pockets. Come back and see me when you've made a bit of room.

Message.SourceString: Oh? You've overburdened yourself with all the random things you can cram in your pockets. Come back and see me when you've made a bit of room.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh? You've overburdened yourself with all the random things you can cram in your pockets. Come back and see me when you've made a bit of room.

Message.SourceString: Why don't you go and give it a proper go right now? Go harvest some crops and then come back and see me. I'll give you a little something for your efforts.
Message.LocalizedString: Why don't you go and give it a proper go right now? Go harvest some crops and then come back and see me. I'll give you a little something for your efforts.

Message.SourceString: Here, take these to get you started.
Message.LocalizedString: Here, take these to get you started.

Message.SourceString: What would you like to know?
Message.LocalizedString: What would you like to know?

Message.SourceString: First, you'll need to build a farming plot. Use a spade on it to clear it of weeds. Once it's completely clear, you're ready to plant.
Message.LocalizedString: First, you'll need to build a farming plot. Use a spade on it to clear it of weeds. Once it's completely clear, you're ready to plant.

Message.SourceString: Just grab the seeds in your hand, and then whack em into the soil. No need for grace, or ceremony, just whomp them in and they'll be fine.
Message.LocalizedString: Just grab the seeds in your hand, and then whack em into the soil. No need for grace, or ceremony, just whomp them in and they'll be fine.

Message.SourceString: Grab yourself a watering can, fill it with water at a water source, and then liberally douse your patch until it's fully soaked through.
Message.LocalizedString: Grab yourself a watering can, fill it with water at a water source, and then liberally douse your patch until it's fully soaked through.

Message.SourceString: Make sure to water your plants every day, ideally first thing in the morning, to keep them nice and healthy.
Message.LocalizedString: Make sure to water your plants every day, ideally first thing in the morning, to keep them nice and healthy.

Message.SourceString: Plants are like people, they need water to survive. You'll want to keep your plants nice and hydrated, so that they don't succumb to disease.
Message.LocalizedString: Plants are like people, they need water to survive. You'll want to keep your plants nice and hydrated, so that they don't succumb to disease.

Message.SourceString: Compost improves the yield on your crops when you harvest them. They simply love to spread their roots around in the stinky stuff.
Message.LocalizedString: Compost improves the yield on your crops when you harvest them. They simply love to spread their roots around in the stinky stuff.

Message.SourceString: To make compost, you'll first need to build a Compost Bin. Then you'll want to fill it with compostible ingredients, like weeds, unwanted logs or irritating exes.
Message.LocalizedString: To make compost, you'll first need to build a Compost Bin. Then you'll want to fill it with compostible ingredients, like weeds, unwanted logs or irritating exes.

Message.SourceString: Give it a little time for the newly added stuff to rot down into compost and then take a Compost Bucket and fill it up.
Message.LocalizedString: Give it a little time for the newly added stuff to rot down into compost and then take a Compost Bucket and fill it up.

Message.SourceString: Then just pour the contents of your bucket over the farming plot, making sure it's spread over it as fully as possible.
Message.LocalizedString: Then just pour the contents of your bucket over the farming plot, making sure it's spread over it as fully as possible.
